      "content": "<!-- wp:heading -->\n<h2 class=\"wp-block-heading\">Summer Cookout Plan</h2>\n<!-- /wp:heading -->\n<!-- wp:paragraph -->\n<p>Invite neighbors for a relaxed cookout with clear prep, serving, and cleanup roles.</p>\n<!-- /wp:paragraph -->\n<!-- wp:list -->\n<ul><!-- wp:list-item --><li>Confirm shared tables, coolers, and vegetarian options.</li><!-- /wp:list-item --><!-- wp:list-item --><li>Assign setup, grill, games, and cleanup volunteers.</li><!-- /wp:list-item --></ul>\n<!-- /wp:list -->\n<!-- wp:buttons -->\n<div class=\"wp-block-buttons\"><!-- wp:button --><div class=\"wp-block-button\"><a class=\"wp-block-button__link\">Share the Plan</a></div><!-- /wp:button --></div>\n<!-- /wp:buttons -->"
